passages.text:
The coffee this morning is even more bitter than usual. You sip it anyway and look at the mountain of paperwork (link-reveal:"on your desk.")[

You take the top sheet, red pen at hand.

//Our cream (link:"can")[(color:red)[could]] keep aging at bay.//

(click:"can")[You take another sip of [[burnt coffee.->Rule 2 Intro]]]
]

//This car (set: $word1 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word1");'>$word1</tw-link></mark> get you there faster than any other.//

//Can't beat the winter blues? You (set: $word2 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word2");'>$word2</tw-link></mark> with Dopraxycaine.//

//The same great taste from our iconic bottle, now in a cute (set: $word3 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word3");'>$word3</tw-link></mark>//

Move on to the [[next sheets of paper.->next sheets of paper. Work]]

(set: $day to 1)

//(set: $word4 to "We urgently need donations to help fund our new hospice. Whoever wins the election, we will also use your donations to fight for more doctors.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["We urgently need donations to help fund our new hospice. Whoever wins the election, we will also use your donations to fight for more doctors.", "We urgently need donations to help fund our new hospice."]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word4");'>$word4</tw-link></mark>//
|alert1>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert1)[(alert:"Health Foundation is a medical charity that provides bursaries to medical students and funds hospitals, hospices and care homes. Approximately twenty percent of its funding is spent on lobbying the government on health issues.")]}

//The drink that (set: $word5 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word5");'>$word5</tw-link></mark> improve your brain power.//

//The real question is, (set: $word6 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word6");'>$word6</tw-link></mark> you afford not to buy this book?//

Before you leave for the day, [[your superior calls you over.->your superior.]]

//Three weeks later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 2")]

(set: $day to 2)

//Crooked teeth? Our dentists (set: $word1 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word1");'>$word1</tw-link></mark> get you smiling again.//

//Open a (set: $word2 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word2");'>$word2</tw-link></mark> of sardines and you (set: $word3 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word3");'>$word3</tw-link></mark> win a holiday.//

//The shirt that (set: $word4 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word4");'>$word4</tw-link></mark> get you the girls. Now in blue.//

You stifle a yawn as (link-reveal:"your boss walks past.")[

He looks tired too. You reach for [[the next sheet of paper.->Day 2 Work 2]]]

//(set: $word5 to "Democracy is under threat. Donate to the Association of Democratic Lawyers today to help save it.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Democracy is under threat. Donate to the Association of Democratic Lawyers today to help save it.", "Donate to the Association of Democratic Lawyers today.", "Reject ad entirely."]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word5");'>$word5</tw-link></mark>//
|alert1>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{
(click: ?alert1)[(alert: "This group was set up during the election campaign ostensibly to support the causes of marginalised groups and the democratic process. Their communications have solely been aimed at the new President and his government.")]}

//Is your mattress over seven years old? Time for a change. Buy the Dormo mark 2 and you (set: $word6 to "can")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["can", "could"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word6");'>$word6</tw-link></mark> get a great night's sleep again.//

//(set: $word7 to "Doctors Across Borders need your help. Donate today and help people in need across the world.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Doctors Across Borders need your help. Donate today and help people in need across the world.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word7");'>$word7</tw-link></mark>//
|alert2>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{
(click: ?alert2)[(alert: "Doctors Across Borders was founded with the aim of sending doctors into countries in dire healthcare situations, for example war, famine, widespread disease. They are politically neutral.")]}

At the end of the day you place your amended papers on your boss' desk and [[head for the station.->Result 2]]

//Two weeks later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 3")]

(set: $day to 3)

//One month later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 4")]

(set: $day to 4)

//Two weeks later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 5")]

(set: $day to 5)

//One week later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 6")]

(set: $day to 6)

//Three weeks later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 7")](stop:)

(set: $day to 7)

//A few days later...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 8")]

(set: $day to 8)

//The next day...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 9")]

(set: $day to 9)

//The following day...//

(live:2s)[(goto: "Journey to 10")]

(set: $day to 10)

//(set: $word1 to "Need a new typewriter? Need one that is world-class and guaranteed for five years? We have just the type for you.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Need a new typewriter? Need one that is world-class and guaranteed for five years? We have just the type for you.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word1");'>$word1</tw-link></mark>//
|alert1>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert1)[(alert:"Arsene Mechanical are a domestic manufacturer of typewriters, printing machinery and telephones. Ninety five percent of their sales are domestic, with five percent exported to South Africa.")]}

//(set: $word2 to "A beach. A soul. Two hearts. Discover the new fragrance from Davide Lille. Discover Heaven.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["A beach. A soul. Two hearts. Discover the new fragrance from Davide Lille. Discover Heaven.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word2");'>$word2</tw-link></mark>//
|alert2>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert2)[(alert:"Davide Lille was a French company, now owned by a Bangladeshi parent company. Most of their perfumes are outsourced to a small family perfumery. Attempts to diversify into the fashion industry have so far failed.")]}

//(set: $word3 to "Can you reach a mind? Can you expand a horizon? Can you take a hand when it needs help? Then teach.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Can you reach a mind? Can you expand a horizon? Can you take a hand when it needs help? Then teach.","Could you reach a mind? Could you expand a horizon? Could you take a hand when it needs help? Then teach.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word3");'>$word3</tw-link></mark>//
|alert3>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert3)[(alert:"The National Teachers' Union represents the interests of their members in pay discussions, employment disputes and political negotiations. In the last financial year seventy percent of their spending was on political campaigning. NTU banners were prominently displayed at the recently banned anti-government protests.")]}

You check the time. Somehow it's only (link-reveal:"lunch.")[ Today it's a spicy tomato soup with crusty bread from the lunch cart. The lady always gives you extra bread.]

After you've eaten you pour another terrible coffee and [[get back to work.->Day 3 Work 2]]

//(set: $word4 to "If you are bringing home the bacon, bring home the best.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["If you are bringing home the bacon, bring home the best.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word4");'>$word4</tw-link></mark>//
|alert1>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert1)[(alert:"Danish Meats Corp is a Chinese company specialising in reformed meat products. They are the world's number one company for pig-based products, number four for cow and number six for chicken.")]}

//(set: $word5 to "Give domestic abuse nowhere to hide. Every five pounds can help someone escape a violent relationship.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Give domestic abuse nowhere to hide. Every five pounds can help someone escape a violent relationship.", "Give domestic abuse nowhere to hide. Every five pounds could help someone escape a violent relationship.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word5");'>$word5</tw-link></mark>//
|alert2>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert2)[(alert:"Safe Homes is a domestic charity that oversees a number of shelters where women and men can stay to escape violent partners. More than half of their time and funding is spent lobbying the government for state run shelters and tougher punshments for repeat offenders.")]}

//(set: $word6 to "The home of ancient wisdom. The home of modern technology. The home of great flavours. Visit India, the home you never knew you had.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["The home of ancient wisdom. The home of modern technology. The home of great flavours. Visit India, the home you never knew you had.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word6");'>$word6</tw-link></mark>//
|alert3>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert3)[(alert:"Visit India is the Indian government's tourism promotion arm. They run organised tours, bespoke trips and itineraries to suit individuals or groups. This year is the year of Indian cuisine and a number of culinary tours have been heavily discounted.")]}

Thanks to the new rules you have to work (link-reveal:"half an hour later than usual.")[ When you take your papers to your boss he gives a (link-reveal:"sympathetic grimace.")[

(color:#E88666)[Maybe it won't be for much longer.]

You (link-reveal:"grunt agreement")[, unsure if he meant that the government would be changing the rules soon, or [[won't last much longer.->Day 3 Result]]]]]

//(set: $word1 to "The shirt that can get you the girls. Now in salmon.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["The shirt that can get you the girls. Now in salmon.", "The shirt that could get you the girls. Now in salmon.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word1");'>$word1</tw-link></mark>//
|alert1>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert1)[(alert:"White and Sons is a family run business with factories in India, Pakistan and Indonesia. The head office is in The Netherlands.")]}

//(set: $word2 to "When the unthinkable happens, we will be there for you.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["When the unthinkable happens, we will be there for you.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word2");'>$word2</tw-link></mark>//
|alert2>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert2)[(alert:"Virtuoso is a trading name for the Heinlich & co insurance group. Heinlich & co are a German corporation, the largest insurance group in Europe.")]}

//(set: $word3 to "Doctors Across Borders need your help. Donate today and help people in need across the world.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Doctors Across Borders need your help. Donate today and help people in need across the world.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word3");'>$word3</tw-link></mark>//
|alert3>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert3)[(alert:"Doctors Across Borders was founded with the aim of sending doctors into countries in dire healthcare situations, for example war, famine, widespread disease. They are politically neutral and based in France.")]}

You're ravenous (link-reveal:"when the lunch cart comes.")[

The usual lady isn't working today, and when you ask after her the replacement (link-reveal:"just shrugs.")[

You try not to get crumbs from your roll [[all over your desk.->Day 4 Work 3]]]]

//It's ok. (set: $advice to "It was just rhetoric to win the election")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["It was just rhetoric to win the election", "There are checks and balances", "Nothing ever really changes", "There is no cause to be paranoid", "You must admit, immigration has got out of hand over the last few years"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$advice");'>$advice</tw-link></mark>.//

//Everything will carry on just fine.//

//(if: $politicalview is "you have always got on ok")[Besides, we've always got on ok, [haven't we?]<next|](elseif: $politicalview is "you find it boring")[Anyway politics is dull, have you tried [that restaurant I recommended?]<next|](elseif: $politicalview is "they are all as bad as each other")[Anyway, they're all [as bad as each other.]<next|](else:)[[Nothing will come of it.]<next|]//

(click: ?next)[(goto: "conversation ends")]

//It's ok. (set: $advice to "It was just rhetoric to win the election")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["It was just rhetoric to win the election", "There are checks and balances", "Nothing ever really changes", "There is no cause to be paranoid", "You must admit, immigration has got out of hand over the last few years"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$advice");'>$advice</tw-link></mark>.//

//Everything will carry on just fine.//

//(if: $politicalview is "you have always got on ok")[Besides, we've always got on ok, [haven't we?]<next|](elseif: $politicalview is "you find it boring")[Anyway politics is dull, have you tried [that restaurant I recommended?]<next|](elseif: $politicalview is "they are all as bad as each other")[Anyway, they're all [as bad as each other.]<next|](else:)[[Nothing will come of it.]<next|]//

(click: ?next)[(goto: "friend conversation ends")]

There's (link-reveal:"no stamp.")[
(set: $letter to true)
//Dear government employee

Please note that in this time of heightened national security it is necessary to protect our democracy. As a beneficiary of a government salary your actions must uphold the high standards expected by the President and our people.

It has come to our attention that your behaviour is not always aligned with the goals of our great nation. Please attend to this immediately. 

Behaviour such as:
Poor work;
Not adhering to government-mandated rules;
Associating with persons of low moral character;
Associating with persons of interest to the state;

Will not be tolerated. Your behaviour has been reported to this department by a member of the public who must remain anonymous. On investigation we have found the complaint to be reasonable.

We look forward to your behaviour improving in future. Further complaints will be dealt with severely.//

You take several deep breaths and [[as many drinks.->envelope 2]]]

//(set: $word4 to "Know your neighbours. Good neighbours mean good communities.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Know your neighbours. Good neighbours mean good communities.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word4");'>$word4</tw-link></mark>//
|alert1>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert1)[(alert:"The Department for the Interior is the goverment department concerned with domestic affairs. This awareness campaign is intended to foster community spirit.")]}

//(set: $word5 to "Meaty Chunks by Buddy contain all the nutrients to help keep your best pal healthy, happy and wagging.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Meaty Chunks by Buddy contain all the nutrients to help keep your best pal healthy, happy and wagging.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word5");'>$word5</tw-link></mark>//
|alert2>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert2)[(alert:"Buddy is the country's number one petcare brand. Their CEO is a prominent businessman known for his flamboyant lifestyle and personal dislike of animals.")]}

//(set: $word6 to "The watch to set all other watches by. Made in Switzerland.")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["The watch to set all other watches by. Made in Switzerland.", "Reject ad entirely"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$word6");'>$word6</tw-link></mark>//
|alert3>[(text-style:"subscript")[<span class='dimLink'>About the advertiser</span>]]
{(click:?alert3)[(alert:"Drotex manufacture top of the line watches and sponsor a number of high profile sporting events. One small element of the workings is made in Switzerland, but most of the watch is made at their main factory in Indonesia, also the site of their head office.")]}

By the time you've finished your stack of work you're hungry again. You hand your papers to your boss and [[head home for something to eat.->Day 4 result]]

(color:#76FF70)[There is a piece of paper in front of you. Please write down the names or descriptions of any dissidents you know. If you help our enquiries we may consider a more lenient sentence. Or perhaps forget all about this misunderstanding.]

You pick up the red pen. The tip hovers above the page, as it has done (link-reveal:"so many times before.")[

1. {(if: $family is > 0)[(set: $name1 to "Your brother and his wife")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Your brother and his wife", "Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name1");'>$name1</tw-link></mark>](else:)[(set: $name1 to "Leave blank")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name1");'>$name1</tw-link></mark>]}
2. {(if: $friend is > 0)[(set: $name2 to "Your university lecturer friend")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Your university lecturer friend", "Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name2");'>$name2</tw-link></mark>](else:)[(set: $name2 to "Leave blank")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name2");'>$name2</tw-link></mark>]}
3. {(if: $protest is true)[(set: $name3 to "The clumsy lady from the train")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["The clumsy lady from the train", "Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name3");'>$name3</tw-link></mark>](else:)[(set: $name3 to "Leave blank")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name3");'>$name3</tw-link></mark>]}
4. {(if: $bar is true)[(set: $name4 to "The patrons of the resistance bar")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["The patrons of the resistance bar", "Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name4");'>$name4</tw-link></mark>](else:)[(set: $name4 to "Leave blank")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name4");'>$name4</tw-link></mark>]}
5. {(if: $suspectboss is true)[(set: $name5 to "Your boss")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["The clumsy lady from the train", "Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name5");'>$name5</tw-link></mark>](else:)[(set: $name5 to "Leave blank")<mark><tw-link class='cyclingLink' data-cycling-texts='["Leave blank", "Fuck you"]' onclick='clickCyclingLink(this, "$name5");'>$name5</tw-link></mark>]}

When you're finished you push the paper across the desk (link-reveal:"to the officers.")[ 

[[They stare at what you've written.->Sentence Results]]
]]
